174
00:16:25,724 --> 00:16:27,791
她必须吃掉那一整颗心吗?
She has to eat the whole heart?

175
00:16:28,759 --> 00:16:30,626
我希望那不是我的马.
I hope that wasn't my horse.

176
00:16:30,662 --> 00:16:32,495
她做得很好.
She's doing well.

177
00:16:32,529 --> 00:16:34,530
她吃不下的.
She'll never keep it down.

178
00:16:34,566 --> 00:16:36,700
