Rakh! Rakh! Rakh haj!

179
00:16:36,735 --> 00:16:39,235
<i>(王子骑着马!)
Khalakka Dothrae!</i>

180
00:16:55,922 --> 00:16:55,988
<i>(王子骑着马!)
Khalakka Dothrae!</i>

181
00:16:57,956 --> 00:16:59,857
告诉我她在说什么.
Tell me what she's saying.

182
00:16:59,892 --> 00:17:02,394
"王子骑着马.
"The prince is riding.

183
00:17:02,427 --> 00:17:05,429
我听见他的蹄声隆隆.
I have heard the thunder of his hooves.

184
00:17:05,463 --> 00:17:07,865
他的马迅捷如风.
Swift as the wind he rides.

185
00:17:09,299 --> 00:17:12,169
他的敌人将在他面前颤抖...
His enemies will cower before him...

186
00:17:13,636 --> 00:17:17,140
敌人的妻子们将悲伤泣血."
And their wives will weep tears of blood."

187
00:17:20,878 --> 00:17:23,013
她将生下一个男孩.
She's going to have a boy.

188
00:17:25,750 --> 00:17:28,386
他不会是一个真正的坦格利安.
He won't be a real Targaryen.

189
00:17:28,421 --> 00:17:30,823
他不会是一条真龙.
He won't be a true Dragon.

190
00:18:21,209 --> 00:18:24,178
<i>(骑着世界的骏马!)
Vezh fin saja rhaesheseres!</i>

191
00:18:24,211 --> 00:18:27,314
"骑着世界的骏马."
"The stallion who mounts the world."

192
00:18:27,348 --> 00:18:30,351
那骏马将是卡奥中的卡奥.
The stallion is the Khal of Khals.

193
00:18:30,384 --> 00:18:33,487
他将统一所有的卡拉萨.
He shall unite the people into a single Khalasar.

194
00:18:33,521 --> 00:18:36,890
<i>全世界的人都将属于他.
All the people of the world will be his herd.</i>

195
00:18:36,924 --> 00:18:39,125
<i>(...骑着世界!)
...Rhaesheseres!</i>

196
00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:41,327
<i>(骑着世界!)
Rhaesheseres!</i>

197
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:44,327
<i>(王子在我体内骑马!)</i>

198
00:18:44,559 --> 00:18:48,327
<i>(他的名字叫做雷戈!)</i>

199
00:18:49,538 --> 00:18:52,038
雷戈! 雷戈!
Rhaego! Rhaego!

200
00:18:52,073 --> 00:18:54,208
雷戈! 雷戈!
Rhaego! Rhaego!

201
00:18:54,241 --> 00:18:57,009
雷戈! 雷戈...
Rhaego! Rhaego...

202
00:19:03,150 --> 00:19:05,750
他们爱戴她.
They love her.

203
00:19:08,354 --> 00:19:09,586
雷戈! 雷戈!
Rhaego! Rhaego!

204
00:19:09,622 --> 00:19:12,356
雷戈! 雷戈...
Rhaego! Rhaego...

205
00:19:29,742 --> 00:19:32,845
今天她是一位真正的王后了.
She truly is a queen today.

206
00:20:01,138 --> 00:20:04,642
别让他们看到你在维斯多斯拉克带着剑.
Don't let them see you carrying a sword in Vaes Dothrak.

207
00:20:04,675 --> 00:20:06,809
你知道这违反律法.
You know the law.

208
00:20:06,844 --> 00:20:08,811
这律法管不着我.
It's not my law.

209
00:20:08,846 --> 00:20:10,815
它们不是属于你的.
They don't belong to you.

210
00:20:10,848 --> 00:20:13,250
她的东西都是属于我的.
Whatever is hers is also mine.

211
00:20:14,153 --> 00:20:15,921
或许曾经属于你.
Once, perhaps.

212
00:20:17,856 --> 00:20:20,692
如果我卖掉一颗龙蛋, 就足够买一条船.
If I sell one egg, I'll have enough to buy a ship.

213
00:20:20,727 --> 00:20:22,894
卖两颗... 一条船加一支军队.
Two eggs... a ship and an army.

214
00:20:22,930 --> 00:20:26,231
- 你拿了三颗. - 我需要一支大军.
- And you have all three. - I need a large army.

215
00:20:27,602 --> 00:20:30,403
我是一个王朝复兴最后的希望, 莫尔蒙.
I'm the last hope of a dynasty, Mormont.

216
00:20:30,438 --> 00:20:32,573
世界上古往今来最伟大的王朝
The greatest dynasty this world has ever seen

217
00:20:32,606 --> 00:20:35,108
自五岁起我就担负着这项使命...
on my shoulders since I was five years old...

218
00:20:35,143 --> 00:20:38,144
却从没人给予我在那帐篷里他们所给予她的东西.
and no one has ever given me what they gave to her in that tent.

219
00:20:38,179 --> 00:20:40,047
从来没有.
Never.

220
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:42,315
一点也没有.
Not a piece of it.

221
00:20:42,349 --> 00:20:45,018
没有这些我如何能履行我的使命?
How can I carry what I need to carry without it?

222
00:20:45,051 --> 00:20:46,752
嗯?
Hmm?

223
00:20:46,787 --> 00:20:49,221
没有财富或恐惧或爱戴如何能进行统治?
Who can rule without wealth or fear or love?

224
00:20:53,558 --> 00:20:57,463
哦, 你站在那里, 又高贵又荣誉.
Oh, you stand there, all nobility and honor.

225
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:03,336
你以为我没发现你是用何种眼神看着我的妹妹, 嗯?
You don't think I see you looking at my little sister, hmm?

226
00:21:03,371 --> 00:21:05,906
你以为我不知道你想要什么?
Don't think I know what you want?

227
00:21:08,943 --> 00:21:11,846
我无所谓. 你可以拥有她.
I don't care. You can have her.

228
00:21:11,881 --> 00:21:14,148
她可以当蛮子的王后并且尽情...
She can be Queen of the savages and dine

229
00:21:14,183 --> 00:21:16,117
享用那最美味的马的器官,
on the finest bloody horseparts,

230
00:21:16,152 --> 00:21:18,953
你也可以尽情享用她的任何器官.
and you can dine on whichever parts of her you like.

231
00:21:20,288 --> 00:21:22,624
让我走吧.
But let me go.

232
00:21:24,792 --> 00:21:26,294
你可以走.
You can go.

233
00:21:26,327 --> 00:21:28,162
但你不能带走龙蛋.
You can't have the eggs.

234
00:21:28,195 --> 00:21:29,962
你曾向我宣誓效忠.
You swore an oath to me.

235
00:21:29,998 --> 00:21:32,499
忠诚对你来说不值一提吗?
Does loyalty mean nothing to you?

236
00:21:32,532 --> 00:21:34,701
那是我的一切.
It means everything to me.

237
00:21:34,734 --> 00:21:36,736
然而你还是站在这里.
And yet here you stand.

238
00:21:36,769 --> 00:21:38,871
所以我还是站在这里.
And yet here I stand.

239
00:21:54,822 --> 00:21:57,423
莫德!
Mord!

240
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:59,692
莫德!
Mord!

241
00:22:02,095 --> 00:22:03,962
莫德!
Mord!

242
00:22:07,667 --> 00:22:09,701
莫德!
Mord!

243
00:22:10,703 --> 00:22:12,505
莫德.
Mord.

244
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:15,540
又在吵闹了!
Noise again!

245
00:22:17,944 --> 00:22:20,747
- 有关那些金子... - 没有金子!
- About the gold... - No gold!

246
00:22:20,781 --> 00:22:23,217
- 没有金子. - 听我说!
- No gold. - Listen to me!

247
00:22:23,250 --> 00:22:25,318
听我说.
Listen to me.

248
00:22:25,353 --> 00:22:27,555
有时候财产
Sometimes possession

249
00:22:27,588 --> 00:22:29,691
是个抽象的概念...
is an abstract concept...

250
00:22:31,728 --> 00:22:34,262
他们抓我的时候拿走了我的钱包,
When they captured me, they took my purse,

251
00:22:34,297 --> 00:22:36,265
但那些金子还是我的.
but the gold is still mine.

252
00:22:36,298 --> 00:22:38,067
在哪儿?
Where?

253
00:22:38,101 --> 00:22:40,201
在哪儿? 我不知道在哪儿,
Where? I don't know where,

254
00:22:40,236 --> 00:22:41,536
但等他们给我自由的时候...
but when they free me...

255
00:22:41,570 --> 00:22:42,971
你想要自由?
You want free?

256
00:22:43,905 --> 00:22:46,240
那儿有自由.
Go be free.

257
00:22:47,509 --> 00:22:49,676
你有没有听说过这句话
Have you ever heard the phrase

258
00:22:49,711 --> 00:22:51,644
"象兰尼斯特家一样有钱"?
"rich as a Lannister"?

259
00:22:54,249 --> 00:22:56,250
<i>你当然听说过!
Of course you have!</i>

260
00:22:56,284 --> 00:22:59,220
你是个聪明人.
You're a smart man.

261
00:22:59,253 --> 00:23:02,089
你知道兰尼斯特家.
You know who the Lannisters are.

262
00:23:02,991 --> 00:23:05,960
我就是兰尼斯特家的.
I am a Lannister.

263
00:23:05,994 --> 00:23:09,663
泰温之子提利昂!
Tyrion, son of Tywin!

264
00:23:09,699 --> 00:23:13,769
而且, 你当然也听说过这句话,
And of course, you have also heard the phrase,

265
00:23:13,804 --> 00:23:17,140
"兰尼斯特有债必还."
"a Lannister always pays his debts."

266
00:23:18,942 --> 00:23:21,510
如果你替我传个口信...
If you deliver a message from me...

267
00:23:22,613 --> 00:23:25,981
给艾林夫人, 就算我欠你一笔债.
to Lady Arryn, I will be in your debt.

268
00:23:27,750 --> 00:23:30,086
我会给你很多金子.
I will owe you gold.

269
00:23:31,455 --> 00:23:33,589
如果你传了口信
If you deliver the message

270
00:23:33,625 --> 00:23:37,461
如果我活下来了, 我一定会的.
and I live, which I very much intend to do.

271
00:23:40,097 --> 00:23:41,898
什么口信?
What message?

272
00:23:48,573 --> 00:23:51,208
告诉她我打算认罪.
Tell her I wish to confess my crimes.

273
00:23:57,583 --> 00:24:00,617
你打算认罪?
You wish to confess your crimes?

274
00:24:00,653 --> 00:24:02,287
是的, 夫人.
Yes, My Lady.

275
00:24:02,320 --> 00:24:03,855
我愿意, 夫人.
I do, My Lady.

276
00:24:03,888 --> 00:24:07,224
天牢可以让任何人屈服.
The sky cells always break them.

277
00:24:07,259 --> 00:24:09,461
说吧, 小恶魔.
Speak, Imp.

278
00:24:09,496 --> 00:24:11,896
坦诚地面对诸神吧.
Meet your gods as an honest man.

279
00:24:16,701 --> 00:24:20,338
该从何说起呢, 各位大人和夫人?
Where do I begin, my lords and ladies?

280
00:24:21,641 --> 00:24:23,509
我是个坏蛋,
I'm a vile man,

281
00:24:23,542 --> 00:24:25,443
我承认这一点.
I confess it.

282
00:24:25,478 --> 00:24:28,480
我犯下的罪过数不胜数.
My crimes and sins are beyond counting.

283
00:24:28,515 --> 00:24:31,650
<i>我撒过谎骗过人...
I have lied and cheated...</i>

284
00:24:32,984 --> 00:24:35,119
<i>赌过钱嫖过妓.
gambled and whored.</i>

285
00:24:36,823 --> 00:24:38,790
<i>我不是特别擅长暴力,
I'm not particularly good at violence,</i>

286
00:24:38,825 --> 00:24:42,260
但我擅长鼓动他人替我施暴.
but I'm good at convincing others to do violence for me.

287
00:24:44,898 --> 00:24:47,032
我想你是想听具体一点的.
You want specifics, I suppose.

288
00:24:48,435 --> 00:24:50,971
七岁那年, 我看见一个女仆
When I was seven I saw a servant girl

289
00:24:51,005 --> 00:24:52,972
在河里洗澡.
bathing in the river.

290
00:24:53,008 --> 00:24:54,875
我偷走了她的衣服.
I stole her robe.

291
00:24:54,909 --> 00:24:57,242
于是她不得不...
She was forced to return to the castle

292
00:24:57,278 --> 00:24:59,278
光着身子哭着回城堡.
naked and in tears.

293
00:25:00,881 --> 00:25:02,614
如果我闭上眼睛,
If I close my eyes,

294
00:25:02,648 --> 00:25:05,851
还能看见她跳动的乳头.
I can still see her tits bouncing.

295
00:25:08,119 --> 00:25:12,355
十岁那年, 我在我叔叔的靴子里塞满羊粪.
When I was 10 I stuffed my Uncle's boots with goatshit.

296
00:25:12,391 --> 00:25:14,791
<i>别人问我的时候,
When confronted with my crime,</i>

297
00:25:14,826 --> 00:25:17,295
我归咎于一个侍从. 那可怜孩子挨了鞭打
I blamed a squire. Poor boy was flogged

298
00:25:17,328 --> 00:25:19,564
而我却逃脱了惩罚.
and I escaped justice.

299
00:25:19,597 --> 00:25:21,365
<i>十二岁那年
When I was 12</i>

300
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:24,402
我朝一锅炖海龟猛挤我那小鳗鱼...
I milked my eel into a pot of turtle stew.

301
00:25:24,436 --> 00:25:27,472
猛扭我那小独眼蛇...
I flogged the one-eyed snake.

302
00:25:27,507 --> 00:25:29,508
猛搓我那小香肠...
I skinned my sausage.

303
00:25:29,542 --> 00:25:32,744
猛揍我那爱哭的小秃子...
I made the bald man cry

304
00:25:32,779 --> 00:25:34,780
<i>给那炖海龟加了点作料,
into the turtle stew,</i>

305
00:25:34,815 --> 00:25:36,816
我相信我老姐把它吃了.
which I do believe my sister ate.

306
00:25:36,849 --> 00:25:38,785
<i>至少我希望她吃了.
At least I hope she did.</i>

307
00:25:38,818 --> 00:25:41,153
有一回我又带了一头公驴和一个蜂窝
Once I brought a jackass and a honeycomb

308
00:25:41,188 --> 00:25:43,355
- 去一家妓院... - 住口!
- into a brothel... - Silence!

309
00:25:43,388 --> 00:25:44,990
后来怎么样了?
What happened next?

310
00:25:45,991 --> 00:25:49,026
你以为你在干什么?
What do you think you're doing?

311
00:25:49,060 --> 00:25:50,994
我在认罪啊.
Confessing my crimes.

312
00:25:51,028 --> 00:25:53,564
提利昂大人, 你被控
Lord Tyrion, you are accused

313
00:25:53,597 --> 00:25:57,067
雇人行刺我卧病在床的儿子布兰,
of hiring a man to slay my son Bran in his bed,

314
00:25:57,102 --> 00:25:59,904
<i>以及密谋害死我妹妹的丈夫
and of conspiring to murder my sister's husband</i>

315
00:25:59,939 --> 00:26:03,776
琼恩艾林大人, 国王之手.
Lord Jon Arryn, the Hand of the King.

316
00:26:03,809 --> 00:26:06,144
哦, 我非常抱歉.
Oh, I'm very sorry.

317
00:26:07,314 --> 00:26:09,249
我对这些一无所知.
I don't know anything about all that.

318
00:26:10,384 --> 00:26:12,619
你的玩笑开够了.
You've had your little joke.

319
00:26:12,653 --> 00:26:15,022
我相信你玩得很愉快.
I trust you enjoyed it.

320
00:26:15,057 --> 00:26:17,925
莫德, 带他回地牢.
Mord, take him back to the dungeon.

321
00:26:17,960 --> 00:26:20,294
这次找个更小的房间...
But this time find a smaller cell...

322
00:26:20,328 --> 00:26:22,430
而且地板也更斜的.
With a steeper floor.

323
00:26:22,464 --> 00:26:25,232
难道这就是所谓
Is this how justice

324
00:26:25,267 --> 00:26:27,134
艾林谷的正义?
is done in the Vale?

325
00:26:27,169 --> 00:26:29,737
<i>你指控我有罪,
You accuse me of crimes,</i>

326
00:26:29,771 --> 00:26:32,940
我否认有罪, 所以你把我扔进牢房
I deny them, so you throw me into a cell

327
00:26:32,973 --> 00:26:34,842
<i>冻饿而死?
to freeze and starve?</i>

328
00:26:34,875 --> 00:26:37,811
国王的正义到哪里去了?
Where is the King's Justice?

329
00:26:37,846 --> 00:26:41,215
既然我遭到指控, 我要求公平审判!
I am accused and demand a trial!

330
00:26:42,951 --> 00:26:44,886
如果你被判有罪,
If you're tried and found guilty,

331
00:26:44,921 --> 00:26:48,023
那么依照国王的律法你只有死路一条.
then by the King's own laws you will pay with your life.

332
00:26:48,057 --> 00:26:51,161
我尊重律法.
I understand the law.

333
00:26:51,194 --> 00:26:53,762
我们鹰巢城没有刽子手.
We have no executioner in the Eyrie.

334
00:26:53,798 --> 00:26:56,599
我们这里有更文雅的法子.
Life is more elegant here.

335
00:26:56,634 --> 00:26:58,567
打开月门.
Open the moon door.

336
00:27:19,221 --> 00:27:22,190
<i>你想要一场审判, 兰尼斯特大人.
You want a trial, My Lord Lannister.</i>

337
00:27:22,223 --> 00:27:24,224
很好.
Very well.

338
00:27:24,259 --> 00:27:27,228
我儿子会倾听你要说的话,
My son will listen to whatever you have to say,

339
00:27:27,262 --> 00:27:29,529
而你将接受他的判决.
and you will hear his judgment.

340
00:27:29,565 --> 00:27:31,665
然后你就可以离开...
Then you will leave...

341
00:27:31,701 --> 00:27:33,835
从这道门或那道门.
By one door or the other.

342
00:27:33,868 --> 00:27:37,070
不必惊动罗宾大人了.
No need to bother Lord Robin.

343
00:27:37,105 --> 00:27:40,741
我要求比武审判.
I demand a trial by combat.

344
00:27:49,384 --> 00:27:51,251
你当然有这个权利.
You have that right.

345
00:27:52,320 --> 00:27:54,221
夫人, 我请您恩准.
My Lady, I beg the honor.

346
00:27:54,256 --> 00:27:56,223
让我做您的代理骑士.
Let me be your champion.

347
00:27:56,258 --> 00:27:58,659
这份荣幸应该归我所有.
The honor should be mine.

348
00:27:58,693 --> 00:28:00,928
看在我对您夫君敬爱有加的份上,
For the love I bore your Lord husband,

349
00:28:00,962 --> 00:28:02,763
让我替他报仇罢.
let me avenge his death.

350
00:28:02,798 --> 00:28:05,333
<i>- 我愿为您而战, 夫人. - 这将是我的荣幸.
- I'll fight for you, My Lady. - It'll be my honor.</i>

351
00:28:05,366 --> 00:28:08,701
- 这将是我的荣幸. - 让这坏蛋飞!
- The honor should be mine. - Make the bad man fly!

352
00:28:09,971 --> 00:28:12,673
