in the name of our King, Robert.</i>

450
00:33:38,605 --> 00:33:41,940
贝里唐德利恩大人.
Lord Beric Dondarrion.

451
00:33:45,978 --> 00:33:49,681
你立刻率领一百名士兵
You shall have the command. Assemble 100 men

452
