the first of his name,

455
00:34:03,663 --> 00:34:07,532
安达尔人与先民的国王, 七国统治者
King of the Andals and the first men, Lord of the Seven Kingdoms

456
00:34:07,567 --> 00:34:09,802
暨全境守护者之名,
and protector of the realm,

457
00:34:09,836 --> 00:34:12,070
我命令你实施国王的正义
I charge you to bring the King's Justice

458
00:34:12,106 --> 00:34:14,141
处置虚伪的骑士格雷果克里冈
to the false knight Gregor Clegane

459
00:34:14,175 --> 00:34:16,643
