and attaint him.

462
00:34:20,614 --> 00:34:23,916
褫夺其一切官阶及头衔,
I strip him of all ranks and titles,

463
00:34:23,952 --> 00:34:27,619
<i>一切封地及财产,
of all lands and holdings,</i>

464
00:34:27,655 --> 00:34:31,023
- 并判处其死刑. - 大人...
- and sentence him to death. - My Lord...

465
00:34:31,057 --> 00:34:34,025
这... 这是一项重大的举措.
This... this is a drastic action.

466
00:34:34,061 --> 00:34:36,829
最好先等劳勃国王回来.
It would be better to wait for King Robert's return.

467
00:34:36,864 --> 00:34:39,297
- 派席尔大学士. - 大人.
- Grand Maester Pycelle. - My Lord.

468
00:34:39,333 --> 00:34:41,702
送一只渡鸦去凯岩城.
Send a raven to Casterly Rock.

469
