Enough, Ser Vardis! Finish him.

485
00:37:40,322 --> 00:37:43,090
<i>你怎么了? 站起来!
What are you doing? Get up!</i>

486
00:37:43,125 --> 00:37:46,193
<i>站起来, 站起来, 站起来!
Get up, get up, get up!</i>

487
00:37:48,228 --> 00:37:50,431
<i>快举剑. 举剑!
Raise your sword. Raise it!</i>

488
00:37:53,735 --> 00:37:55,335
