Get up, man!

489
00:37:55,369 --> 00:37:57,070
<i>- 快站起来! - 起来!
- On your feet! - Get up!</i>

490
00:37:57,105 --> 00:37:59,739
<i>起来战斗, 瓦狄斯爵士!
Get up and fight, Ser Vardis!</i>

491
