Now you are being rude.

519
00:41:00,356 --> 00:41:02,492
王子.
My prince.

520
00:41:04,795 --> 00:41:06,762
王子.
My prince.

521
00:41:06,797 --> 00:41:08,398
小姐.
My Lady.

522
00:41:09,634 --> 00:41:11,967
我恐怕表现得有些粗暴
I fear I have behaved monstrously

523
00:41:12,003 --> 00:41:14,871
