like the one your mother wears.

527
00:41:36,257 --> 00:41:38,224
有朝一日你将成为王后.
You'll be queen someday.

528
00:41:38,259 --> 00:41:41,061
你必须打扮得象个王后.
It's only fitting you should look the part.

529
00:41:45,701 --> 00:41:48,235
你能原谅我的粗鲁吗?
Will you forgive me for my rudeness?

530
00:41:48,271 --> 00:41:51,206
没什么要原谅的.
There's nothing to forgive.

531
00:41:52,909 --> 00:41:55,612
你是我亲爱的小姐.
You're My Lady.

532
00:41:55,646 --> 00:41:58,815
有朝一日我们会在朝堂上举行婚礼.
One day we'll be married in the throne room.

533
00:41:58,849 --> 00:42:02,784
七国各地的领主和夫人们都会赶来,
Lords and ladies from all over the Seven Kingdoms will come,

534
00:42:02,818 --> 00:42:05,086
从最北端城堡
from the last hearth in the North

535
00:42:05,121 --> 00:42:08,056
到最南端的海滨,
to the Salt Shore in the South,

536
00:42:08,090 --> 00:42:11,327
你将是他们最高贵的王后.
and you will be Queen over all of them.

537
00:42:14,563 --> 00:42:16,998
<i>我永远不会再对你无礼.
I'll never disrespect you again.</i>

538
00:42:17,032 --> 00:42:20,235
我也永远不会再对你粗暴.
I'll never be cruel to you again.

539
00:42:20,268 --> 00:42:22,570
你明白吗?
Do you understand me?

540
00:42:24,407 --> 00:42:26,641
你是我亲爱的小姐,
You're My Lady now,

541
00:42:26,675 --> 00:42:30,112
从今天开始
from this day

542
00:42:30,146 --> 00:42:32,914
直到我生命的最后一天.
until my last day.

543
00:42:55,005 --> 00:42:57,106
停下.
Stop.

544
00:42:57,141 --> 00:42:59,710
- 停下! - 哦哇.
- Stop! - Whoa.

545
00:43:01,112 --> 00:43:03,646
- 你在干什么? - 去君临.
- What are you doing? - Going to King's Landing.

546
00:43:03,681 --> 00:43:05,782
乘一辆运芜菁的车子?
In a turnip cart?

547
00:43:05,815 --> 00:43:08,818
我会在白港找一条去南方的船.
I'll find a ship heading south in White Harbor.

548
00:43:09,885 --> 00:43:11,686
你付得起船钱吗?
And you can afford that?

549
00:43:11,721 --> 00:43:14,422
我的一些朋友比另一些慷慨.
Some of my friends are more generous than others.

550
00:43:14,456 --> 00:43:17,125
君临有上千象你这样的姑娘.
There's a thousand girls like you in King's Landing.

551
00:43:17,159 --> 00:43:19,427
那我会有很多同伴.
So I'll have lots of company.

552
00:43:19,461 --> 00:43:21,163
是的, 你会很受欢迎...
Yes, you'll be very popular...

553
00:43:21,197 --> 00:43:22,898
直到哪一天某个肥胖的领主光临
Until some fat lord comes to visit

554
00:43:22,932 --> 00:43:24,800
肚子很大而那话儿很小
with a big belly and a little prick

555
00:43:24,835 --> 00:43:27,336
因为你伺候得他不满意, 把你打得满地找牙.
and he can't get it up so he knocks all your teeth out.

556
00:43:27,371 --> 00:43:30,239
我留在这里会怎样?
And what will happen to me if I stay here?

557
00:43:30,273 --> 00:43:32,208
我会成为葛雷乔伊夫人吗,
Will I become Lady Greyjoy,

558
00:43:32,242 --> 00:43:35,313
- 会成为铁群岛的女主人吗? - 别傻了.
- mistress of the Iron Islands? - Don't be a fool.

559
00:43:35,347 --> 00:43:37,481
我听说詹姆兰尼斯特攻击了史塔克大人
I hear Jaime Lannister attacked Lord Stark

560
00:43:37,516 --> 00:43:39,282
就在君临城的大街上.
in the streets of King's Landing.

561
00:43:39,318 --> 00:43:43,186
很快方圆百里的所有男人都将从军南下
Every man for a hundred miles will be marching off to war soon

562
00:43:43,221 --> 00:43:45,188
他们多数永远都不会再回来.
and most of them will never come back.

563
00:43:45,222 --> 00:43:47,224
这儿没我什么事了.
There's nothing left for me here.

564
00:43:48,492 --> 00:43:50,559
我们走吧, 斯特芬.
Let's go, Stefon.

565
00:43:50,594 --> 00:43:52,061
<i>走喽.
Giddyup.</i>

566
00:43:52,094 --> 00:43:54,362
让我再看一眼!
Let me see it one more time!

567
00:43:54,396 --> 00:43:56,697
看什么?
See what?

568
00:44:08,110 --> 00:44:10,210
我会想念你的.
I'm going to miss you.

569
00:44:10,246 --> 00:44:12,112
我知道.
I know.

570
00:44:25,893 --> 00:44:27,927
我要送你们俩回临冬城.
I'm sending you both back to Winterfell.

571
00:44:27,961 --> 00:44:29,362
- 什么?! - 听我说...
- What?! - Listen...

572
00:44:29,396 --> 00:44:31,998
- 乔佛里的事怎么办? - 因为你的腿伤好不了吗?
- What about Joffrey? - Are you dying because of your leg?

573
00:44:32,032 --> 00:44:33,311
<i>所以你要送我们回家?
Is that why you're sending us home?</i>

574
00:44:33,335 --> 00:44:34,500
什么? 不是.
What? No.

575
00:44:34,501 --> 00:44:35,934
求你了, 父亲. 不要.
Please, father. Please don't.

576
00:44:35,969 --> 00:44:38,137
不可以. 我要跟西利欧上课.
You can't. I've got my lessons with Syrio.

577
00:44:38,170 --> 00:44:39,771
我一定会表现好的.
I'm finally getting good.

578
00:44:39,806 --> 00:44:42,240
这不是在惩罚你们.
This isn't a punishment.

579
00:44:42,275 --> 00:44:44,677
我让你们回临冬城是为你们的安全着想.
I want you back in Winterfell for your own safety.

580
00:44:44,710 --> 00:44:46,144
我们可以带西利欧一起走吗?
Can we take Syrio back with us?

581
00:44:46,179 --> 00:44:47,751
谁管你的笨舞蹈老师啊?
Who cares about your stupid dancing teacher?

582
00:44:47,775 --> 00:44:49,076
我不能走.
I can't go.

583
00:44:49,083 --> 00:44:50,951
我是要嫁给乔佛里王子的.
I'm supposed to marry Prince Joffrey.

584
00:44:50,985 --> 00:44:52,887
我爱他, 我要做他的王后
I love him and I'm meant to be his Queen

585
00:44:52,920 --> 00:44:55,523
- 为他生孩子. - 七层地狱啊.
- and have his babies. - Seven hells.

586
00:44:55,556 --> 00:44:57,190
等你再大点,
When you're old enough,

587
00:44:57,224 --> 00:44:59,927
我会给你找个配得上你的人,
I'll make you a match with someone who's worthy of you,

588
00:44:59,961 --> 00:45:02,630
既勇敢又温柔又强壮...
someone who's brave and gentle and strong...

589
00:45:02,664 --> 00:45:05,934
我不要什么勇敢温柔又强壮的人. 我只要他!
I don't want someone brave and gentle and strong. I want him!

590
00:45:05,967 --> 00:45:08,737
他会成为最伟大的国王, 如同黄金雄狮,
He'll be the greatest King that ever was, a golden lion,

591
00:45:08,771 --> 00:45:11,539
我会为她生下拥有漂亮金发的儿女.
and I'll give him sons with beautiful blond hair.

592
00:45:11,574 --> 00:45:14,208
<i>他才不是狮子, 白痴.
The lion'sot s Sigil, idiot.</i>

593
00:45:14,242 --> 00:45:16,043
他是鹿, 象他父亲一样.
He's a stag, like his father.

594
00:45:16,077 --> 00:45:18,980
他才不是. 他一点也不象那个酒鬼国王.
He is not. He's nothing like that old drunk King.

595
00:45:22,184 --> 00:45:25,019
去吧, 孩子们. 让修女帮你们收拾东西.
Go on, girls. Get your Septa and start packing your things.

596
00:45:25,054 --> 00:45:26,556
- 等等! - 来吧.
- Wait! - Come on.

597
00:45:26,590 --> 00:45:28,224
但这不公平!
But it's not fair!

598
00:46:02,661 --> 00:46:05,664
"欧瑞斯拜拉席恩, 黑发."
"Lord Orys Baratheon, black of hair."

599
00:46:07,800 --> 00:46:10,570
"阿克谢尔拜拉席恩, 黑发."
"Axel Baratheon, black of hair."

600
00:46:11,672 --> 00:46:14,474
"莱昂内尔拜拉席恩, 黑发."
"Lyonel Baratheon, black of hair."

601
00:46:15,844 --> 00:46:18,612
"斯蒂芬拜拉席恩, 黑发."
"Steffon Baratheon, black of hair."

602
00:46:24,050 --> 00:46:26,652
"劳勃拜拉席恩, 黑发."
"Robert Baratheon, black of hair."

603
00:46:28,655 --> 00:46:30,856
"乔佛里拜拉席恩...
"Joffrey Baratheon...

604
00:46:31,923 --> 00:46:34,025
金发."
Golden-haired."

605
00:47:05,590 --> 00:47:07,492
丹妮莉丝!
Daenerys!

606
00:47:09,829 --> 00:47:11,764
我妹妹在哪儿?
Where's my sister?

607
00:47:11,798 --> 00:47:12,965
拦住他.
Stop him.

608
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:14,534
<i>她在哪儿?
Where is she?</i>

609
00:47:14,568 --> 00:47:16,702
<i>嗯?
Hmm?</i>

610
00:47:19,172 --> 00:47:21,940
她在哪儿? 我来参加宴会.
Where is she? I'm here for the feast.

611
00:47:23,010 --> 00:47:25,277
- 那烂女人的宴会? - 来.
- The whore's feast? - Come.

612
00:47:25,311 --> 00:47:26,978
把你的手拿开!
Get your hands off me!

613
00:47:27,012 --> 00:47:29,547
谁也不能触碰真龙!
No one touches the Dragon!

614
00:47:30,416 --> 00:47:32,583
<i>(酸腿国王!)
Khal rhae mhar!</i>

615
00:47:32,617 --> 00:47:35,385
(他来了!)
Me ifa!

616
00:47:38,023 --> 00:47:40,492
卓戈卡奥!
Khal Drogo!

617
00:47:40,527 --> 00:47:42,994
我是来参加宴会的.
I'm here for the feast.

618
00:47:44,030 --> 00:47:47,800
<i>(你的位子在那儿.)
Nevakhi vekha ha maan.</i>

619
00:47:47,835 --> 00:47:50,202
卓戈卡奥说你的座位在那里.
Khal Drogo says there is a place for you.

620
00:47:50,237 --> 00:47:52,438
那个地方.
Back there.

621
00:47:54,675 --> 00:47:56,911
那不是给国王坐的地方.
That is no place for a King.

622
00:47:56,945 --> 00:47:59,612
你不是国王.
You are no King.

623
00:48:01,849 --> 00:48:04,016
离我远点!
Keep away from me!

624
00:48:04,050 --> 00:48:06,052
韦赛里斯, 求你了.
Viserys, please.

625
00:48:08,188 --> 00:48:10,088
原来她在这儿.
There she is.

626
00:48:14,460 --> 00:48:17,295
把剑收起来. 这会把我们全害死的.
Put the sword down. They'll kill us all.

627
00:48:17,329 --> 00:48:19,965
他们奈何不了我们.
They can't kill us.

628
00:48:21,300 --> 00:48:24,001
他们不能在他们的圣城里流血.
They can't shed blood in their sacred city.

629
00:48:31,077 --> 00:48:32,512
但我能.
But I can.

630
00:48:42,255 --> 00:48:44,690
我只想要属于我的东西.
I want what I came for.

631
00:48:44,724 --> 00:48:47,126
我只想要他答应我的那顶王冠.
I want the crown he promised me.

632
00:48:47,994 --> 00:48:49,896
他买了你.
He bought you.

633
00:48:49,929 --> 00:48:52,063
但他从未付钱.
But he never paid for you.

634
00:48:57,269 --> 00:49:00,338
告诉他我要完成交易, 否则我就要收回你.
Tell him I want what was bargained for or I'm taking you back.

635
00:49:01,407 --> 00:49:04,010
他可以留下孩子.
He can keep the baby.

636
00:49:04,043 --> 00:49:06,344
我会把它割下来给他.
I'll cut it out and leave it for him.

637
00:49:09,583 --> 00:49:12,818
<i>(......)
Anha vazhak maan rek me zala.</i>

638
00:49:14,255 --> 00:49:17,590
<i>(......)
Anha vazhak maan firikhnharen hoshora</i>

639
00:49:17,625 --> 00:49:20,360
<i>(......)
ma mahrazhi aqovi affin mori atihi mae!</i>

640
00:49:20,393 --> 00:49:22,829
他说什么?
What's he saying?

641
00:49:24,264 --> 00:49:25,998
他说好的.
He says yes.

642
00:49:27,434 --> 00:49:30,335
你将拥有一顶黄金王冠...
You shall have a golden crown...

643
00:49:31,972 --> 00:49:34,539
任谁看了都会颤抖.
That men shall tremble to behold.

644
00:49:45,684 --> 00:49:47,885
我要的就只是这个.
That was all I wanted.

645
00:49:50,255 --> 00:49:52,389
他答应要给我的.
What-what was promised.

646
00:50:08,873 --> 00:50:10,840
<i>(抓住他.)
Qora mae.</i>

647
00:50:12,110 --> 00:50:14,143
不!
No!

648
00:50:14,179 --> 00:50:16,880
不! 你们不准碰我.
No! You cannot touch me.

649
00:50:16,914 --> 00:50:19,250
我是真龙. 我是真龙!
I am the Dragon. I am the Dragon!

650
00:50:19,284 --> 00:50:22,052
我要我的王冠! 啊!
I want my crown! Ahh!

651
00:50:22,088 --> 00:50:25,257
<i>(拿锅来!)
Ammeni haz jolin!</i>

652
00:50:34,300 --> 00:50:36,603
- 请你转过头, 卡丽熙. - 不.
- Look away, Khaleesi. - No.

653
00:50:43,577 --> 00:50:45,945
<i>不, 丹妮.
No, dany.</i>

654
00:50:45,978 --> 00:50:47,445
丹妮, 告诉他们.
Dany, tell them.

655
00:50:47,480 --> 00:50:48,914
告诉他们!
Make them!

656
00:50:49,916 --> 00:50:52,684
<i>丹妮, 让他们...
Dany, make them...</i>

657
00:50:54,353 --> 00:50:56,454
不, 你不能!
No, you can't!

658
00:50:56,489 --> 00:50:59,625
只要... 求你了!
Just... please!

659
00:50:59,659 --> 00:51:02,594
丹妮, 求你了!
Dany, please!

660
00:51:04,197 --> 00:51:06,699
国王的王冠.
A crown for a King.

661
00:51:21,681 --> 00:51:24,050
卡丽熙?
Khaleesi?

662
00:51:24,083 --> 00:51:26,286
他不是真龙.
He was no Dragon.

663
00:51:27,454 --> 00:51:30,090
真龙不怕火.
Fire cannot kill a Dragon.

